{
  "stem": "22979.7",
  "chunk_idx": 7,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 9.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "But when I applied for a job in 1951-- after my second child was born, we couldn't live from one salary-- they didn't take me.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "First I went, because I had already my education at [INAUDIBLE] what they ask for being able to work in a bookstore.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So the manager said, oh, we need [INAUDIBLE] So well, yes, you can come tomorrow, because we need badly somebody here.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So I said, fine.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But here is, he said, a questionnaire.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "You have to fill it out.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I filled out.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I filled out where I was during war, what my religion is, everything.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And when he looked at the application, he said, we don't need no more.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Because he didn't want me, because I was a Jewish.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So what did I do?",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Next time, I went for application, I didn't fill out the column my religion.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I didn't fill out where I was during the war.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I was accepted.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "In the same store?",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Pardon?",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "In the same store.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I worked there for 15 years until we came back.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "It was the Communists was softer.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Dubcek was there already.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And, you know, it was, you know, you know, somehow, the [INAUDIBLE], the younger generation didn't want to be so, you know, I mean, one sided, I would say.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They were more open.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "They had the chance more to get to the West, to read.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So it was, like he said, they wanted Communism with a human face.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I didn't worship at all.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We didn't have a Jewish community there.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "What you talking?",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "We didn't have a rabbi.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "We didn't have kosher.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "We didn't have nothing.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Who'd returned?",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And who returned left the country.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Many legal-- I never wanted illegal.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Many left and were-- were shot on the borders.",
      "word_count": 9
    }
  ],
